                            <comment id="14158164" author="jinghe" created="Fri, 3 Oct 2014 16:34:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The configuration steps are probably similar to or overlap with the set up for Rest security and impersonation support.&lt;br/&gt;
But it is not clear.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14158175" author="jxiang" created="Fri, 3 Oct 2014 16:42:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Have you checked the refguid, section 8.1.6, 8.1.7? &lt;a href=&quot;http://hbase.apache.org/book/security.html#hbase.secure.configuration&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://hbase.apache.org/book/security.html#hbase.secure.configuration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
How should we improve it? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14158194" author="jinghe" created="Fri, 3 Oct 2014 17:02:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jxiang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jxiang&quot;&gt;Jimmy Xiang&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Yes.&lt;br/&gt;
We can improve the sections, and/or add a section to mention SPNEGO-based authentication for client.&lt;br/&gt;
I am trying to set it up.  After that, I probably will have more input.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14161722" author="misty" created="Tue, 7 Oct 2014 10:10:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please feel free to document this as you go, or at least take notes and leave them here.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14317204" author="jinghe" created="Wed, 11 Feb 2015 23:29:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached a patch for the documentation update, also a screen capture of what is generated in the book.&lt;br/&gt;
The documentation update mentions the support for custom Authentication handlers in Rest gateway.&lt;br/&gt;
I had a custom Authentication handler and it was tested to work well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14317220" author="jinghe" created="Wed, 11 Feb 2015 23:41:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ping &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=apurtell&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;apurtell&quot;&gt;Andrew Purtell&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jxiang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jxiang&quot;&gt;Jimmy Xiang&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=misty&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;misty&quot;&gt;Misty Stanley-Jones&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks in advance for any review!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
